<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="DisableSmartcard" version="5.0">
 <title xml:id="SecurityServices">Disable Smart Card Support</title>
 <para>
  Disable the pcscd service which provides support for smart cards and
  smart card readers.
  <indexterm>
   <primary>Smart Card</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <indexterm>
   <primary>pcscd</primary>
  </indexterm>
 </para>
